data.description: This home is in a newer subdivision-lots of new construction still happening. It is a French Style home and owner says it's on the biggest lot on their street. Back yard is fully fenced with a wood fence. Home has an open floor plan and kitchen and baths have granite counters. Kitchen has a breakfast bar, pantry, gas range and pretty cabinets. Master has walk in closet. Living room has wood floors.
